          "reviewBody": "Unfortunately my both the kids were studying there. It was my biggest mistake to put kids there. Will give them -10 stars.\nPost seeing attitude of teachers, I lost trust and respect on teachers. They disrespect students and parents both.\nMy son suffers with learning disability hence school convinced us rather smartly forced us to switch my son from ICSE to  NIOS board in 8th standard . And we obeyed them like fool. After a year and half in middle of the 9th standard they informed us that they can't continue NIOS and we have to take our son's admission in other school.  Our son was just an experiment for them which didn't work for them.",
